"{\"uid\": \"newser.com-story-353856-olympic-swimmer-emerges-from-pool-collapses.html\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Slovakian swimmer Tamara Potocka collapsed poolside Friday morning after a qualifying heat of the women's 200-meter individual medley at the Paris Olympics.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 156, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 18, \"end\": 24, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tamara_Todevska\", \"score\": 0.9776716100017508, \"rank\": 0.018653029712846794, \"text\": \"Tamara\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tamara_Todevska\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tamara_Todevska\"}, {\"begin\": 25, \"end\": 32, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Potocki_family\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Potocka\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Potocki_family\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Potocki_family\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Potocka, 21, collapsed as she got out of the water and almost immediately was surrounded by a half-dozen medical attendants, who put her on a stretcher after about a minute and carried her off the pool deck, per theAP.\", \"from\": 157, \"to\": 375, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 157, \"end\": 164, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Potocki_family\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Potocka\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Potocki_family\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Potocki_family\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"First aid was administered to Potocka, who was seen wearing an oxygen mask as she was taken away for medical attention.\", \"from\": 376, \"to\": 495, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 406, \"end\": 413, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Potocki_family\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Potocka\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Potocki_family\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Potocki_family\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Medical personal at the pool said she was conscious.\", \"from\": 497, \"to\": 549, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Slovakian officials later said that Potocka had suffered an asthma attack, reportsESPN.\", \"from\": 550, \"to\": 637, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 586, \"end\": 593, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Potocki_family\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Potocka\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Potocki_family\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Potocki_family\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Tamara has asthma,\\\" Slovakian team leader Ivana Lange said in a statement.\", \"from\": 638, \"to\": 713, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"This whole combination of nervous and physical tension while she did not have her inhaler immediately available to use contributed to the creation of this problem.\\\"\", \"from\": 714, \"to\": 879, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Lange added that Potocka was given oxygen and necessary meds, and that \\\"the doctor told me that she must be monitored for several more hours.\\\"\", \"from\": 880, \"to\": 1022, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 897, \"end\": 904, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Potocki_family\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Potocka\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Potocki_family\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Potocki_family\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Medical personal at the pool said she was conscious.\", \"from\": 1024, \"to\": 1076, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Slovakian officials later said that Potocka had suffered an asthma attack, reportsESPN.\", \"from\": 1077, \"to\": 1164, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1113, \"end\": 1120, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Potocki_family\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Potocka\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Potocki_family\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Potocki_family\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Tamara has asthma,\\\" Slovakian team leader Ivana Lange said in a statement.\", \"from\": 1165, \"to\": 1240, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"This whole combination of nervous and physical tension while she did not have her inhaler immediately available to use contributed to the creation of this problem.\\\"\", \"from\": 1241, \"to\": 1406, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Lange added that Potocka was given oxygen and necessary meds, and that \\\"the doctor told me that she must be monitored for several more hours.\\\"\", \"from\": 1407, \"to\": 1549, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1424, \"end\": 1431, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Potocki_family\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Potocka\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Potocki_family\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Potocki_family\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Israeli swimmer Leah Polonsky, who swam two heats after Potocka, said swimmers know their sport has inherent risks.\", \"from\": 1551, \"to\": 1666, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1551, \"end\": 1558, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israel_Defense_Forces\", \"score\": 0.7944721602936653, \"rank\": 0.21344625474572773, \"text\": \"Israeli\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q176799\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israel_Defense_Forces\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israel_Defense_Forces\"}, {\"begin\": 1567, \"end\": 1571, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leah_Patterson-Baker\", \"score\": 0.8190925564408488, \"rank\": 0.14385809378361825, \"text\": \"Leah\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leah_Patterson-Baker\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leah_Patterson-Baker\"}, {\"begin\": 1607, \"end\": 1614, \"ti